<
py.Model.optimize
<! type method
<! brief
<Optimize this model.
<! arg paramdict: Optional[Dict[str, ArrayLike]] = {}
<The constant value to be bounded to parameter.
<! arg tuner: Optional[Callable[[TuningContext], None]] = None
<The customized hyper parameter tuning function.
<
<! example
<```py
<def hptune(ctx: TuningContext):
<    print(ctx)
<
<p = Param("param1", 2, 2)
<x = Var(2, 2)
<
<model.setObjective(sum(p @ x))
<model.optimize({"param1": [[1, 2], [3, 4]]}, hptune)
<```
<
<
py.Model.removeConstr
<! type method
<! sortname constrR
